<span class="n">${arr.length}/5</span></h2>${arr.map(cellHTML).join('')||'<div class="gap">空</div>'}</div>`;
const perfReady=Object.keys(PERF).length>0;
document.getElementById('root').innerHTML=`
<h1>三分法池 · 总览
<span class="quota ${full?'full':''}">本月迁移 <b>${q}/${lim}</b> 对${full?' · 已达上限':''}</span></h1>
<div class="sub">last_modified ${esc(POOL.last_modified)} · schema ${esc(POOL.schema_version)} · 15 只 = V${ps.v}+T${ps.t}+N${ps.n}
${perfReady?'':' · <span style="color:var(--warn)">涨跌加载中(首次约 1-2 分钟,15min 缓存)</span>'}</div>
<div class="cols">${col('V',POOL.v_pool)}${col('T',POOL.t_pool)}${col('N',POOL.n_pool)}</div>

<div class="sec"><h3>配对迁移(两腿原子 · TECH §10.3)</h3>
<div class="hint">池规模锁定 5+5+5(I4.1),满员时<b>不能单加</b>——必须一出一进原子执行。点击上方票选择:<b>第一次点=出腿</b>,<b>第二次点=入腿</b>,再点同一只取消。</div>
<div class="legs">
<div class="leg exit ${SEL.exit?'on':''}"><div class="lab">出腿(离开原类)</div>
${SEL.exit?`<div class="who">${esc(SEL.exit.name)} <span class="tk">${esc(SEL.exit.ticker)}</span></div>
<div class="path">${esc(SEL.exit.category)} → <select id="exit-to" style="width:auto;display:inline-block">
${['V','T','N'].filter(x=>x!==SEL.exit.category).map(x=>`<option value="${x}">${x}</option>`).join('')}</select></div>`
:'<div class="ph">未选择 · 点击上方任一票</div>'}</div>
<div class="leg enter ${SEL.enter?'on':''}"><div class="lab">入腿(进入目标类)</div>
${SEL.enter?`<div class="who">${esc(SEL.enter.name)} <span class="tk">${esc(SEL.enter.ticker)}</span></div>
<div class="path">${esc(SEL.enter.category)} → <select id="enter-to" style="width:auto;display:inline-block">
${['V','T','N'].filter(x=>x!==SEL.enter.category).map(x=>`<option value="${x}">${x}</option>`).join('')}</select></div>`
:'<div class="ph">未选择 · 再点池内另一只票</div>'}</div>
</div>
<div class="hint" style="border-left:2px solid var(--warn);padding-left:10px;margin-top:10px">
<b style="color:var(--warn)">池外新票入腿暂不可用。</b> 当前 <code>execute_migration_pair</code> 仅支持池内 <b>V/T/N 三类互迁</b>
(两腿方向必须互补,各池净变化 = 0);<code>MigrationLeg</code> 的类别域为 <code>Literal['V','T','N']</code>,不含 <code>OUT</code>。
TECH §10.3 规格含 OUT,实现待补。<br>
进出池当前只能:<b>目标类未满员</b> → 下方单票加池;<b>已满员</b> → 先移出一只再加(注意:会经过瞬时 4/5 中间态)。</div>
<label class="f">迁移理由(必填,I4.5——不填后端直接拒绝 MissingMigrationRationale)</label>
<textarea id="rationale" placeholder="写清楚为什么迁:触发了什么信号 / 依据哪些数据点"></textarea>
<div class="tmpl" id="tmpl"></div>
<div class="act"><button class="primary" id="btn-mig" disabled>提交配对迁移</button>
<button class="ghost" id="btn-clear">清除选择</button>
<span class="why-block" id="mig-why"></span></div>
<div id="mig-msg"></div></div>

<div class="sec"><h3>单票操作(仅在目标类未满员时)</h3>
<div class="single">
<div><div class="hint">加池 —— 目标类 &lt;5 才允许。<b>满员时会被 400 拒绝</b>(I4.1)。</div>
<div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 80px;gap:8px;margin-top:8px">
<input id="add-tk" placeholder="ticker"><input id="add-nm" placeholder="名称">
<select id="add-cat"><option>V</option><option>T</option><option>N</option></select></div>
